{"tid":1192833,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日對香港嘅廢老改觀","createTime":"2019-06-08T15:32:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T16:21:57.000Z","uid":3749,"like":49,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6c3c5466d4c54f6930c5ef6619c3ffa471712b37","tid":1192833,"uid":3749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T15:32:17.000Z","msg":"今日放工經過公園，有班廢老走過黎問我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：喂，細佬，聽日出唔出黎啊！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：（我果陣諗係唔係問我聽日出唔出去）出啊，點都出<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：香港靠哂你地啦，後生仔，啊叔骨頭脆，做唔到啲咩野出黎架啦。<br />\n<br />\n係果一刻，我覺得唔係所有廢老都親共。<br />\n番到屋企，我就準備聽日6.9嘅野，屋企兩老入黎我間房<br />\n同我講<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：仔啊，雖然我地唔識野，唔知點做先最好，但係我地支持你，放心去啦，我聽日煲定湯等你番黎飲。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：係呢一刻，我感受到好多人嘅支持，我聽日一定會平平安安咁去，平平安安咁番黎，等我番黎飲湯啊媽！<br />\n<br />\n聽日點都要出黎啊！香港人！唔好諗住多你一個唔多，少你一個唔少，你地每一個都好重要！"},{"pid":"2eec601f487f93ecc700e2979f0eea94bd2f75d0","tid":1192833,"uid":23160,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T15:34:18.000Z","msg":"屋企果件垃圾依然睇贏國初音就當自己睇透全世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4fd563dbf05c2c5c4135b28e509242c9db59c9e","tid":1192833,"uid":52230,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T15:34:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>槍口一致對外！<br />\n<br />\n不要分化！不要懷疑隊友！<br />\n<br />\n有人被捕立即群擁而上集體救援！<br />\n<br />\n勿比機會警犬單獨拉走同伴！<br />\n<br />\n一切行動必須群體出發！ <br />\n<br />\nStick Together Team! 不要落單！<br />\n<br />\n6.9 GOGOGO!</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>唔衝嘅人幫手拖住篤灰狗 <br />\n<br />\n衝嘅巴繼續上前！<br />\n<br />\n齊心！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9dfbd52397fd05f2619781fb47c3d6172a33211","tid":1192833,"uid":20449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T15:36:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7ff8f7075aaf947f04659fb34d92a14b359298a1","tid":1192833,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2eec601f487f93ecc700e2979f0eea94bd2f75d0","tid":1192833,"uid":23160,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T15:34:18.000Z","msg":"屋企果件垃圾依然睇贏國初音就當自己睇透全世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T15:36:44.000Z","msg":"-贏國<br />\n-初音<br />\n<br />\nChoose One"},{"pid":"1bdae8b6f7a1f53d54ca077428a64085ceed47e7","tid":1192833,"uid":109602,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T15:38:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"33e036c0d9cfca9e9df06f8cd7e9f06d0ced383a","tid":1192833,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T15:38:57.000Z","msg":"大媽跳淫舞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"071134b72ba668736b0e2a169c81393e419521b7","tid":1192833,"uid":23160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7ff8f7075aaf947f04659fb34d92a14b359298a1","tid":1192833,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2eec601f487f93ecc700e2979f0eea94bd2f75d0","tid":1192833,"uid":23160,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T15:34:18.000Z","msg":"屋企果件垃圾依然睇贏國初音就當自己睇透全世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T15:36:44.000Z","msg":"-贏國<br />\n-初音<br />\n<br />\nChoose One"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T15:39:26.000Z","msg":"機械聲果啲洗腦片呀<br />\n係要講到咁白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown